    <p><strong>A commercial kitchen exhaust hood is not optional — it's a legal requirement for most food businesses in India, and a critical safety system for every professional kitchen.</strong> A properly sized and installed exhaust hood removes smoke, grease-laden vapour, heat, and combustion gases before they accumulate, protecting your staff, your equipment, and your licence. This guide covers everything an Indian food business owner needs to know about commercial exhaust hoods in 2026: types, sizing calculations, materials, fire suppression integration, FSSAI and NOC requirements, price ranges, and top suppliers.</p>

